    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40-2018 at MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates RH prediction accuracy within ±10% across the full COU operating envelope. The assessment team accepted the argument that the sole difference between the validation build (ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2) and the production build (ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7) is a licensing-module documentation patch with no solver kernel impact, and therefore no re-validation was required under the released build. The model is fit for purpose to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
